OL,3,CAstronaut urges world to preserve
OL,4,Coceans after seeing them from space
OL,6,FA NASA astronaut who was struck by the
OL,7,Fbeauty and fragility of Earth during
OL,8,Fher time in space is calling for
OL,9,Fglobal action to tackle the planet's
OL,10,Fmost pressing problems.
OL,12,FAmerican Nicole Stott spent more than
OL,13,Fone hundred days aboard the
OL,14,FInternational Space Station and Space
OL,15,FShuttle, becoming the first person to
OL,16,Fpaint a watercolour in space.
OL,18,FWhen she saw the Earth from space for
OL,19,Fthe first time, Nicole was moved by
OL,20,Fhow nature can support human life.
