OL,3,CAstronaut urges world to preserve
OL,4,Coceans after seeing them from space
OL,6,FWhile Nicole's work has taken her on a
OL,7,Fjourney of galactic proportions, back
OL,8,Fon Earth she believes even the
OL,9,Fsmallest communities have a role to
OL,10,Fplay in protecting the planet.
OL,12,FFor World Oceans Week, she is visiting
OL,13,Fto take part in several events,
OL,14,Fincluding talking to schoolchildren
OL,15,Fabout their environment.
OL,17,FNicole explains: "We're all together
OL,18,Fon this planet, I love coming to
OL,19,Fevents where we're acknowledging our
OL,20,Fplace and the significance of the
OL,21,Focean.
