OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F389A1717665306
OL,3,CAstronaut urges world to preserve
OL,4,Coceans after seeing them from space
OL,6,F"The more we do of this and the more
OL,7,Fkids experience something like this,
OL,8,Fthe more they're going to grow up as
OL,9,Fcrewmates and not passengers.
OL,11,F"That's the biggest message in it all,
OL,12,Fif we choose to behave like crewmates,
OL,13,Fwe can create a future for all life on
OL,14,FEarth that's as beautiful as it looks
OL,15,Ffrom space."
OL,17,FTamsin Raine and Matt Porteous,
OL,18,Ffounders of Jersey conservation
OL,19,Fcharity Ocean Culture Life, organised
OL,20,Fthis week's events.
