OL,3,CAstronaut urges world to preserve
OL,4,Coceans after seeing them from space
OL,6,FTamsin says: "We've got two days of
OL,7,Fworkshops with hundreds of children
OL,8,Fcoming down to enjoy the week of
OL,9,Fcelebrations.
OL,11,F"This is all about celebrating our
OL,12,Foceans, inspiring children to connect
OL,13,Fand understand the ocean because if we
OL,14,Fdon't learn to understand it then how
OL,15,Fcan we protect it?"
OL,17,FOther activities include a live-stream
OL,18,Fview of Jersey from space and a beach
OL,19,Fclean-up.
